  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Coorporative governance: Improving quality on public education in Brazil as from the revision and re-adequation of management processes at FNDE.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to develop and implement methodologies for: 1) monitoring , 2) coorporative education on public governance, 3) risk management, and 4) internal and external control of actions and practices implemented by the FNDE, in order to minimize faults on control and execution of programs and actions on education. In addition, it aims to broadening the technical assistance to social and education councils, working on mechanism of transparency and capacity building for education authorities and the general society mobilized toward the education. As a result, management process implemented by FNDE will be optimized, having the different programs being executed integratedly.</narrative>
  </description>
